{"tid":544783,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"已知機箱某到漏電導致開唔到機，但點知係邊到","createTime":"2018-01-30T01:17:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T16:21:19.000Z","uid":108347,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"897a391546a43d918970bd2d269ef0bdef62aa1c","tid":544783,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:17:21.000Z","msg":"之前已基本肯定係機箱有漏電，開唔到機只要郁下d線試下，又會開到，直到拖地撞到又有機會開唔番<br />\n<br />\n但係我點先可以知係邊到出事？本身硬件唔太識，叫人整都唔知點叫，一陣佢話而家開到就掉番比我都係嘥錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83d2b04f9b3c770acb273d5df30802986295ec6d","tid":544783,"uid":39012,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:25:14.000Z","msg":"拆板 就咁放發泡膠上面 開機"},{"pid":"82e28c5b4bcb1a3a22d3f97f5fcdd38dbfbeaf9f","tid":544783,"uid":39012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:26:29.000Z","msg":"其實機箱都係幾舊水姐"},{"pid":"24731f5a51147f03a4320e50041ff5c89433db1d","tid":544783,"uid":147097,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:31:00.000Z","msg":"1. 你點知係漏電? 電親你?<br />\n<br />\n2. 當你真係電, 九成係隻牛, 小機會係底板"},{"pid":"9f54903a2e05112b9d558c70fb9740ab13118852","tid":544783,"uid":3268,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:31:29.000Z","msg":"搵電登佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己用(他）筆 他吓邊到著燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20edac79d776f4b5235be8921437895dde5dc53","tid":544783,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"24731f5a51147f03a4320e50041ff5c89433db1d","tid":544783,"uid":147097,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:31:00.000Z","msg":"1. 你點知係漏電? 電親你?<br />\n<br />\n2. 當你真係電, 九成係隻牛, 小機會係底板"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:35:23.000Z","msg":"因為符合症狀，開唔到時冇咇聲咩都冇，而且開得番唔郁佢成個月都冇事，一郁到唔著時郁下d線會著得番，跟住唔郁佢又會冇事，開住機亦都唔會有野，剩係boot個下先有機會出事"},{"pid":"bda5308363c0d0692b05bf7d2fc804ad51dc2bd3","tid":544783,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"82e28c5b4bcb1a3a22d3f97f5fcdd38dbfbeaf9f","tid":544783,"uid":39012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:26:29.000Z","msg":"其實機箱都係幾舊水姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:36:08.000Z","msg":"我自己唔識換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5af9a5fd07909627d27ff168a940b57c18b09bb0","tid":544783,"uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bda5308363c0d0692b05bf7d2fc804ad51dc2bd3","tid":544783,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"82e28c5b4bcb1a3a22d3f97f5fcdd38dbfbeaf9f","tid":544783,"uid":39012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T01:26:29.000Z","msg":"其實機箱都係幾舊水姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:36:08.000Z","msg":"我自己唔識換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T02:50:33.000Z","msg":"呢度叫巴打畀百五蚊幫你砌咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4cca707ec4360280882159f7fd001a29569af77","tid":544783,"uid":13953,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T03:00:02.000Z","msg":"有冇落銅柱"},{"pid":"989ea979d86c668df17ede614e9df1eb2a351e29","tid":544783,"uid":45189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T03:16:43.000Z","msg":"巴打邊到砌部咁既野返黎架"},{"pid":"ef2e3adda1d4c86f10a431faa8f4a1847f6ca5af","tid":544783,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"989ea979d86c668df17ede614e9df1eb2a351e29","tid":544783,"uid":45189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T03:16:43.000Z","msg":"巴打邊到砌部咁既野返黎架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T03:48:36.000Z","msg":"T記"},{"pid":"e0aafec2ae2de1b4e1a9cc5741819ea89054338a","tid":544783,"uid":143959,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid"